text:
@JDNebusiness vraie question, quelles sont les nouveautés chez Spotify ?

J'ai l'impression que l'app stagne depuis plusieurs années.

Ou même régresse, je suis déçu de mes Discover Weekly Playlist maintenant, alors qu'elles me faisaient découvrir plein de tracks avant...

Fortnite Discovery blocked my island from its initial content testing because another creator updated their island and got into the New and Updated rows first. They ended up claiming the game title, even though it was available when I published. I released my game a day before their update, but they were pushed into the rows before I was.

I worked on this game for months in my spare time. Seeing it dead on launch because of bad luck and the way Discovery works sucks pretty hard, especially after investing time and money into it.

@FNCreate @Flak #UEFN
